data.description: Welcome to 4501 21st Street, a charming and well-maintained home located in the heart of Indianapolis. This delightful residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and affordability, making it an ideal opportunity for first-time homebuyers or savvy investors.  The home includes a full basement, and three bedrooms, each offering a comfortable retreat for rest and relaxation. One well-appointed bathroom equipped with modern fixtures and provide convenience for everyday living. The kitchen is a functional space, featuring ample cabinet storage, sleek countertops, and modern appliances. Don't miss out on the chance to make this delightful residence your own.
